# Enterprise Contact Registry — Party SSOT

## Principle

There is **one** Contacts module (`/contacts`). There is **no** Directory module.

Contacts is the Enterprise Party Registry for every person and company.

## Filters (not menus)

All · Individuals · Companies · role filters from Role Master.

Adding a future role = Role Master entry + automatic filter. No navigation redesign.

## Workspace

One Contact → multiple Roles → one Contact Workspace (tabs from roles).

Companies open Company Workspace from the same registry.

## Data integrity

After Save: registry change bus notifies all consumers. No stale lists. No duplicate contact stores.
